  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BIM Manager (MEP)",
  "description": "<h3>BIM Manager (MEP)</h3>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead BIM implementation, standards, and modelling workflows.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with Project Manager for BIM needs and requirements.</li>\n  <li>Prepare, execute, and maintain the BIM Execution Plan (BEP).</li>\n  <li>Understand project requirements to ensure delivery.</li>\n  <li>Manage design development, documentation, authority submissions, and meetings.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and ensure timely drawing submissions.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate BIM model exchange with consultants, clients, and stakeholders.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s Degree/Postgraduate Diploma in Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Certification in BIM Management.</li>\n  <li>At least 8 years of experience in BIM Management.</li>\n  <li>Strong engineering and design experience.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of Singapore construction regulations.</li>\n  <li>Resourceful and able to work under pressure.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills.</li>\n</ul>",
